{"id": 979, "genre": 1001, "title": "作为一个过来人，你觉得上大学的时候想啥是扯淡？", "description": "现在看来以为重要的事情根本不重要，以为不重要的事情却很要人命。（题图来自：Jenna）", "record_count": 5656, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130035u2EzQ1VJSZdF0ABL.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-07T01:00:16Z", "options": [{"id": 74752, "content": "早上吃哈，中午吃哈，晚上吃哈，吃別人老公鸡巴", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598611}, {"id": 75264, "content": "任何时间想啥都是浪费时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 576915}, {"id": 79104, "content": "一觉醒来发现自己中了500万。大学宿舍的晚上四个人每天都在想", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137185}, {"id": 74753, "content": "想以后到底要做自己喜欢的工作还是工资高的工作…", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 394108}, {"id": 75009, "content": "以为学新闻的我也能辅修金融?", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599512}, {"id": 75265, "content": "是金子在哪儿都会发光的 现在的我不优秀是没人发现我", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 86813}, {"id": 75010, "content": "向男神表白", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 561250}, {"id": 74755, "content": "该考研还是找工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598643}, {"id": 75011, "content": "整天想着创业", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599524}, {"id": 75267, "content": "不努力却憧憬着美好的未来", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 362670}, {"id": 76803, "content": "吊死在一棵树上，没有去看看广阔的森林！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603380}, {"id": 74756, "content": "。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 545913}, {"id": 75012, "content": "把所有课余以外的时间都用在了打工", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599539}, {"id": 75268, "content": "上了大学一定会脱单", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 551773}, {"id": 74757, "content": "觉得专业选的不好，好好学了也没用，这是典型的弱者思维；强者懂得，不管喜欢与否，现在的事情要做得漂亮，才有资格在人生方向确定时，发现自己已经有充分的积累，实现他们的梦想。", "image": null, "praise_count": 146, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 564490}, {"id": 75269, "content": "入党", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600247}, {"id": 76037, "content": "想做自己想做的事，却总是没有行动", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 400464}, {"id": 74758, "content": "很想尝试奇葩食堂菜，可是学校饭堂太正常…", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 588016}, {"id": 75270, "content": "想太多未来的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600230}, {"id": 75271, "content": "自己有一天能打上最强王者", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207518}, {"id": 75016, "content": "每天不多看几眼妹子是不完整的", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 512697}, {"id": 75272, "content": "那个姑娘，我如果努力点应该能追的到。现在想想简直是直男癌。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600236}, {"id": 76040, "content": "谈恋爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601674}, {"id": 74761, "content": "想活着有梦想和期待以后的人生都tm扯淡…", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591690}, {"id": 75273, "content": "还是一名大学生，但是脚踏实地一般都不会后悔", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600246}, {"id": 75274, "content": "实践很重要 社团比学习重要 呵呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 488402}, {"id": 75019, "content": "毕业就结婚", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 578770}, {"id": 75275, "content": "觉得自己以后大有出息，察觉不到自己的平庸", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600248}, {"id": 76811, "content": "所学有所用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 588156}, {"id": 74764, "content": "网恋", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 329164}, {"id": 75276, "content": "中国的大学凭什么需要四年", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120785}, {"id": 74765, "content": "担心有同学会不喜欢自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75414}, {"id": 75021, "content": "大学就应该放开大胆玩，成绩不重要，建立有用的社交圈更重要。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599606}, {"id": 75277, "content": "不来参加的扣学分～扣学分～扣学分～", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598021}, {"id": 74766, "content": "能无限旷课", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504264}, {"id": 75023, "content": "不恋爱不拿奖学金你来大学干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599516}, {"id": 74768, "content": "要不要好好听课", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 593914}, {"id": 75280, "content": "成绩（排名）是不是没那么重要了。。。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589494}, {"id": 77328, "content": "没上过大学～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460959}, {"id": 89360, "content": "想啥都是扯淡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647500}, {"id": 74769, "content": "要考试了。今天去上晚自习，还是玩会儿游戏，明晚再去呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598702}, {"id": 76561, "content": "大一的时候就确定要出国", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273368}, {"id": 74770, "content": "成绩很重要，但逃课不重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569659}, {"id": 75282, "content": "把学生会看得很重要其实是扯蛋", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600257}, {"id": 74771, "content": "那个女同学是不是又喜欢我了", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478685}, {"id": 75283, "content": "自己会成为学神，在学校当中成为风云人物", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599919}, {"id": 74772, "content": "去不去上课\n去不去上课\n去不去上课", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 598714}, {"id": 75028, "content": "明天一定早起，过规律的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 591764}, {"id": 75284, "content": "想以后会很有钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152644}, {"id": 77588, "content": "大一的时候觉得自己的大学一定会很精彩，各种社团活动各种约会各种旅游各种学业优秀。哦，后来发现自己想太多，大学说的最多的就是下课以后吃什么。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 606461}]}